Requirements:
Python 3
fastapi
uvicorn
python-dotenv
httpx

Setup:
Create virtual environment:
python -m venv venv

Activate virtual environment:
Windows:
venv\Scripts\activate

macOS/Linux:
source venv/bin/activate

Install:
pip install -r requirements.txt

Run application:
uvicorn main:app --reload

Open in browser:
http://127.0.0.1:8000/

Stop server:
Ctrl + C

Deactivate environment:
deactivate